text: "I Know What I Like (In Your Wardrobe)" is the first charting single from Genesis. It was taken from their fifth studio album Selling England by the Pound. It was a minor hit and reached number 21 on the single charts in the United Kingdom. ==References== Category:1974 songs Category:Genesis songs Category:Progressive rock songs Category:Psychedelic rock songs
title: I Know What I Like (In Your Wardrobe)
